00:10:49.620 --> 00:10:52.070
some extremely conservative
members of Congress

00:10:52.070 --> 00:10:54.616
who agree on this too,
it's very difficult to do

00:10:54.616 --> 00:10:57.210
and the only way we're
gonna do it is if we get

00:10:57.210 --> 00:11:00.330
big corporations and
the left and the right,

00:11:00.330 --> 00:11:03.640
Democrats and Republicans
to form a coalition

