00:11:13.936 --> 00:11:14.790
- But you know what, I
mean, look, I worked on

00:11:14.790 --> 00:11:16.830
the campaign, I was a
senior economic advisor

00:11:16.830 --> 00:11:19.680
for Donald Trump, what, you know what,

00:11:19.680 --> 00:11:23.290
and I went with him to all
these areas of the country.

00:11:23.290 --> 00:11:25.340
I mean, I heard his speeches
over and over again.

00:11:25.340 --> 00:11:30.270
His most powerful applause
line other than build the wall

00:11:30.270 --> 00:11:34.160
was drain the swamp and Americans, look,

00:11:34.160 --> 00:11:37.440
Americans are much more even
upset about this than you are,

00:11:37.440 --> 00:11:40.390
Bob, I mean, I'll give you
a statistic that I think

00:11:40.390 --> 00:11:43.100
summarizes everything that's
wrong with our government today

00:11:43.100 --> 00:11:45.800
in Washington, I live in
the belly of the beast.

00:11:45.800 --> 00:11:47.030
I live in the swamp.

